<p>The <b>Tocharians</b> were the <a href="/wiki/Tocharian_language" title="Tocharian language" class="mw-redirect">Tocharian</a>-speaking inhabitants of the <a href="/wiki/Tarim_Basin" title="Tarim Basin">Tarim Basin</a>, making them the easternmost speakers of an <a href="/wiki/Indo-European_language" title="Indo-European language" class="mw-redirect">Indo-European language</a> in antiquity.</p>
